Carmen Argenziano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carmen_Argenziano 0 Carmen Antimo Argenziano (born October 27, 1943) is an American actor who has appeared in over 50 movies and around 100 television movies or episodes. He is best known for playing Jacob Carter on Stargate SG-1. He had recurring roles on Booker, L.A. Law, Melrose Place, and The Young and the Restless. He had a small role in The Godfather Part II and The Accused Carmen_Antimo_Argenziano ( born October_27_,_1943 ) is an_American_actor who has_appeared in over_50_movies and around_100_television_movies_or_episodes .
